# .env.example
#
# This project is a static site with no server-side environment variables.
# There are no environment variables to configure for local development.
#
# Forms submit through Web3Forms. The access key is a public form identifier
# (not a secret) and is centralized in:
#   src/js/web3forms-config.js
#
# To rotate the key, edit WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY in that one file — both
# book.html and contact.html import it from there.
